text.title: Evidence Levels
text.short: Current percentage of each level of evidence
text.long: ClinVar variants are associated with a level of evidence representing the strength of the finding. Categories include: not classified, single submitter, expert panel, multiple submitters, professional society.

metadata.author: Lance Pflieger
